          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>A dcpo <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-001S.xml" title="pointed dcpo" addr="jms-001S" type="local">pointed</fr:link> if and only if it is closed under suprema of semidirected subsets.</html:p>
 
   
